    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Magnolia cusucoensis. A–C. Leaf variability in size and shape. A. Kelly et al. CO/4/SS4/320. B. Kelly 970, and C. Kelly & Dietzsch CO/4/SS2/143. D. Hypsophylls. E. Peduncular internodes. F. Developing fruit. G. Gynoecium with broken stigmas, staminal, petal and sepal, and hypsophyll scars. Photographs by A. Vázquez." ;
